Outlier in Rhandsontable

Source: R/routlie_rh.R
routlier_rh.Rd

The outlier will highlighted in green and the word 'Outlier' will replace the value in the cell.

Usage

routlier_rh(data)

Arguments

data

filepath to data

Value

Return's an outlier dataset from the original dataset in an rhandonstable.

Examples



  routlier_rh(data = iris)
#> You have  1  outliers in your dataset
